.kuso

# Embedded VERSION files used to be regenerated at build time and were
# gitignored — but the `*VERSION` glob also matched the case-insensitive
# `version/` directory on macOS APFS, silently swallowing the entire
# `cmd/kusoCli/version/` package from git tracking. We now commit the
# VERSION files and let release.sh rewrite them. Anchored with a
# leading slash so they match files only, not directories.